message.entry: Incorrect number of input arguments. Each parameter name must be followed by a corresponding value.
''BinEdges'' must be a vector of length greater than or equal to 2.
''BinEdges'' input cannot be followed by any of ''NumBins'',''BinWidth'', ''BinMethod'', or ''BinLimits''.
X must be a numeric array.
''integers'' bin method is only supported if the absolute value of each input element is less than or equal to FLINTMAX/2.
''BinEdges'' must be a non-empty, real, numeric vector with no missing values.
''NumBins'' must be a real, finite, positive, integer value.
''BinWidth'' must be a real, finite, positive, numeric scalar.
''BinLimits'' must be a two-element vector of real, finite, positive, numeric values.
Invalid value for ''BinMethod''. Possible values are: ''auto'', ''scott'', ''fd'', ''integers'', ''sturges'', and ''sqrt''.
Invalid value for ''Normalization''. Possible values are: ''count'', ''countdensity'', ''cumcount'', ''probability'', ''pdf'', and ''cdf''.
